snippet.title: [Flash game] Pharaoh's Tomb
snippet.description:
Pharaoh's Tomb is isomatiric view adventure game same as 'gold yard' by francesco maisto released in 2004.
i tried to beat this game with normal mode first but shit was fucking tough so i record easy difficulty first (in higher difficulty you get a higher score)

i thought this game has nice graphic and depth it gives me an exotic feeling

10.19.2021 
https://www.y8.com/games/pharaohs_tomb
you can play this game with y8 browser or flashpoint
